{"tid":1883733,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國軍隊的精英黑客竊取了1300萬英國人的Equifax數據","createTime":"2020-02-17T07:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T09:33:43.000Z","uid":118550,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"852059140ddfc9ee67b330b0ddfbf07db99e975c","tid":1883733,"uid":118550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T07:16:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/chinese-armys-elite-hackers-steal-equifax-data-on-13m-britons-ld32rqjqq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Farticle%2Fchinese-armys-elite-hackers-steal-equifax-data-on-13m-britons-ld32rqjqq&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=cd684f41\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/chinese-armys-elite-hackers-steal-equifax-data-on-13m-britons-ld32rqjqq</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GbCFT0Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGbCFT0Z.jpg&h=3c4d39be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe personal information of more than 13 million Britons was stolen by a team of Chinese military hackers in an elaborate &ldquo;criminal heist&rdquo; spanning the globe.<br />\n<br />\nFour members of the People&rsquo;s Liberation Army (PLA) plundered credit card details, passwords and telephone numbers as part of the biggest state-sponsored theft of individuals&rsquo; private data yet uncovered.<br />\n<br />\nThe Beijing-based hackers, who were identified by the FBI last week, sought to hide their tracks by exploiting a network of computers in almost 20 countries, including Holland and Switzerland.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/AMFChina/status/1228987601442549760?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAMFChina%2Fstatus%2F1228987601442549760%3Fs%3D09&d=Fzfx2iZ%2BI%2BdTugby0OFGQzYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=372a72bb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.